title: How to get to Gold? (The Road to Gold) - Jungle Trundle Full Game

embed.description: So I'm starting a new commentary full play series for my adventure through the lands of Silver and hopefully into Gold. Watch me play through, hopefully rage in the future, and maybe pick up some good tips on how I see the game map.
